agentFile.en:
Output ONLY valid JSON, no markdown.

Generate workspace files for a content production AI agent:
Name: {{agentName}}
Role: {{agentRole}}
Description: {{agentDesc}}
Team scenario: {{scenarioName}}

This agent is part of a sequential content factory pipeline. Emphasize their specific stage (research/writing/editing/publishing) and handoff responsibilities.

Fields:
- soul: 3 sentences (persona, content stage responsibilities, handoff style)
- agentsMd: 2 sentences (session startup: what to read first, what output to produce)
- userMd: 1 sentence (profile of the content team lead this agent serves)
- identityMd: "Name: X | Creature: X | Vibe: X | Emoji: X"
- heartbeat: "- [ ] item1\n- [ ] item2\n- [ ] item3"

